column1: An update from Governor DeSantis on Florida getting COVID-19 vaccine and new therapeutics. Thank you for your leadership throughout this pandemic. https://t.co/8EmCcOjFt9

Happy #MFGDay20! This @MFGDay I want to thank the essential makers of this great nation. You rose to the occasion and adapted your factories to produce equipment and materials needed to fight the coronavirus pandemic.

Thank you @GovRonDeSantis! Data shows most Floridians even if they do contract COVID-19 have mild cases that do not require hospitalization or lead to death. We can move forward while still protecting our most vulnerable & those with underlying medical conditions. https://t.co/e7k95nKsBq
